DIGQueryRoleParentsTranslator
public class DIGQueryRoleAncestorsTranslator
extends DIGQueryTranslator

Translator that generates DIG role ancestors/desendants queries in response to a find queries: 

 :X rdf:subPropertyOf *
 *  rdf:subPropertyOf :X
or similar.
